    What We Offer
  </h2>
  
  <p>Ferni is an AI life coaching service—six specialists who work together to support you through web and phone conversations. We remember your story, understand your patterns, and show up when you need us.</p>
  
  <p><strong>What this means in practice:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personalized guidance</strong> based on your unique situation and goals</li>
    <li><strong>Continuous memory</strong>—we don't forget what matters to you</li>
    <li><strong>Multiple perspectives</strong> from our specialized team members</li>
    <li><strong>Available when you need us</strong>—2am gets the same presence as noon</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="important-boundaries">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
    </span>
    Important Boundaries
  </h2>
  
  <div class="callout callout--important">
    <strong>We're coaches, not clinicians.</strong>
    <p>Ferni is designed for personal development and everyday support—not crisis intervention or professional treatment. We're the friend who really listens, not a replacement for therapists, doctors, or emergency services.</p>
  </div>
  
  <p><strong>We're not equipped to provide:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Medical, psychological, or psychiatric diagnosis or treatment</li>
    <li>Financial, legal, or professional advice</li>
    <li>Emergency or crisis intervention</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p><strong>If you're in crisis:</strong> Please reach out to emergency services (911) or a crisis helpline immediately. Your safety comes first—always.</p>
  
  <p>We'll always try to point you toward appropriate resources when conversations go beyond our scope. That's not us pushing you away; it's us caring enough to know our limits.</p>
</section>

<section id="your-part">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
    </span>
    Your Part in This
  </h2>
  
  <p>Good relationships go both ways. Here's what we ask of you:</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Be yourself.</strong> Share what's real—we can't help with a mask on.</li>
    <li><strong>Use us for good.</strong> Our conversations should help, not harm.</li>
    <li><strong>Keep your access yours.</strong> Your account is personal—don't share credentials.</li>
    <li><strong>Play fair.</strong> Don't try to reverse-engineer, exploit, or misuse our service.</li>
    <li><strong>Respect the team.</strong> We're AI, yes, but we're designed to be treated with the same respect you'd give any coach.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="our-relationship">
  <h2>
    <span class="section-icon">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg>
    </span>
    Our Relationship
  </h2>
  
  <h3>Your Content</h3>
  <p>What you share with us stays between us. We use your conversations to provide personalized coaching—that's it. We never sell your data or use it to train models without explicit consent.</p>
  
  <h3>Our Content</h3>
  <p>Ferni's design, features, and the guidance we provide are our original work, protected by intellectual property laws. Feel free to apply what you learn—that's the whole point—but please don't reproduce our systems or claim them as your own.</p>
  
  <h3>If Things Go Wrong</h3>
  <p>We build with care, but technology isn't perfect. To the extent permitted by law, we're not liable for indirect damages or decisions you make based on our conversations. We're a tool for growth, not a guarantee of outcomes.</p>
  
  <h3>Parting Ways</h3>
  <p>We can end our relationship at any time—you can stop using Ferni, and we can terminate access if these terms are violated. No hard feelings. If we terminate your access, we'll explain why unless doing so would compromise security.</p>
</section>

